ZH: 我们应该尽量少吃油腻的食物。
EN: We should try to eat less greasy food as much as possible.

ZH: 考试前，我会尽量多复习一些重要的知识点。
EN: Before the exam, I will try to review as many important concepts as possible.

ZH: 请你尽量保持安静，我正在集中精力工作。
EN: Please try to keep quiet, I'm trying to concentrate on work.

ZH: 她已经尽量解释了，但是他们还是不理解。
EN: She has tried her best to explain, but they still don't understand.

ZH: 今天我尽量早点下班，希望能和朋友们出去玩。
EN: Today, I'll try to finish work early, hoping to go out and play with friends.

ZH: 天气太差了，我们尽量让室内的活动更有趣。
EN: The weather is so bad, we will try to make indoor activities more fun.

ZH: 尽量把所有的细节都告诉我，这样我才能帮你更好。
EN: Try to tell me all the details, so that I can help you better.

ZH: 明天是个重要的日子，我们尽量不要出差错。
EN: Tomorrow is an important day, let's try not to make any mistakes.

ZH: 在有意见分歧的时候，我们应该尽量保持冷静和理智。
EN: When there are disagreements, we should try to stay calm and rational.

ZH: 路上堵车了，我们只能尽量寻找其他道路。
EN: There's a traffic jam on the road, we can only try to find alternative routes.

ZH: 在写作文时，尽量用简单的语言表达自己的观点。
EN: When writing an essay, try to express your views using simple language.

ZH: 尽量别触碰那件艺术品，它很容易被损坏。
EN: Please try not to touch that artwork, it can be easily damaged.

ZH: 在设计产品时，我们应该尽量考虑用户的需求。
EN: When designing a product, we should try to consider the needs of the users.

ZH: 为了提高生活质量，我们应该尽量减少使用塑料袋。
EN: To improve the quality of life, we should try to reduce the use of plastic bags.

ZH: 物价上涨了，我们只能尽量节约开支。
EN: With the increase in prices, we can only try to save on expenses.

ZH: 父母应该尽量给孩子们提供一个良好的成长环境。
EN: Parents should try their best to provide a good environment for their children to grow up in.

ZH: 在不合适的场合，尽量避免讨论敏感话题。
EN: In inappropriate situations, try to avoid discussing sensitive topics.

ZH: 尽量保持良好的卫生习惯，这样可以预防疾病。
EN: Try to maintain good hygiene habits, which can help prevent diseases.

ZH: 心情不好时，尽量寻找一些让自己开心的事情。
EN: When feeling down, try to find something that makes you happy.

ZH: 在处理问题时，尽量采取合适的方法来解决。
EN: When dealing with problems, try to use appropriate methods to solve them.
